description: Sailmate's "Captain Jack" on Alexa helps you determine if today is a good day to sail.  It considers the weather in your area to determine if the wind is brisk, no wind, or a storm is in the area. It covers major US cities as well as the 101 largest lakes in the US.
exampleInteractions: tell me about the winds in Tampa?
name: Sailmate
shortDescription: Is today going to be a good day to go sailing?
